\p  
\v 1 Agiripa akabh Č Čr…®ra Paaur Č, ‚ÄúUriisiriribhwa kwibhag…®ra.‚ÄĚ 
\p Paaur Č akagorora okobhoko, akatanga kwibhag…®ra arabhuga,  
\v 2 ‚Äú…Ąm Čt…®mi Agiripa, reero niriiyigwa k Čbha n…®n Č  Čr Čbhang Č kwim…®…®r…®ra m Čbh Čtang…® bhwaz Č, korereke nisasaam…® ig Čr Č wa g Č Čsi gan Č Abhayaahudi bhangambir…®.  
\v 3 K…®nda aw…®, k Č k Čbha  Čm…®nyir…® bhwaheene zeteemwa z Č Čsi za Abhayaahudi, na gan Č g Č Čsi bhaar…® bhak Čhakaana, n…®rak Čsabha unyiitegeerere kwa bhwigumirirya. 
\p  
\v 4 ‚ÄúAbhayaahudi bh Č Čsi bh…®…®z…® bhwaheene eteemwa y…®n Č naar…® k Čbha nayo muchar Č chan…®, kw…®ma mubhwana bhwan…®, kuhik…®ra ribhaga r…®n Č niik…®…®r…® Y…®rusar…®…®mu.  
\v 5 Bhaany…®z…® bhwaheene kumyaka myaru, bharaas…®…®g…® bharat Čra kuhurucha obhomenyeekererya, naar…® n…®rakora amanar Č g Č Čsi ga Abhafarisaayo. Abhafarisaayo nebho abhah…®mba bhi imigir Č ja Mungu k Čk…®ra abhand…® bh Č Čsi bh…® …®nyangi y…®…®t Č.  
\v 6 Nang Č k…®n Č kekokora nitinirw…® kumigir Č reero, n…®‚ÄĎk Č k Čbha yu ubhwis…®gi bhwan…® k Čbh Črag…® bh Čn Č Mungu akaragan ľya bhas Č Čk Čr Č.  
