\v 21 Gayo nego gaagiriry…® Abhayaahudi bhangwat…® han Č bhambw…®n…® mwihekaaru, bhakeenda kunyita.  
\v 22 Kuhika reero Mungu ansakiiry…®, ak Črir…® nimiiriir…® nereerekeererya abhaat Č bh Č Čsi abhasuuhu na abhak Čr Č. N…®tak Čbh…®raku amang ľana agand…®, nawe gan Č n…®k Čgamba n…®‚ÄĎgan Č Musa na abhar Č Čt…®r…®ri abhand…® bhagambir…® k Čbha garakorwa.  
\v 23 Bh Č Čsi bhakabhuga, areenderwa Kiriisit Č anyaakibhw…® na k Čbha we embere kury Čka m Čbhaku, korereke areete ubhw…®r Č bhw Č  Čbh Čt…®mi bhwa Mungu k ČBhayaahudi na k Čbhaat Č bhan Č bhatar…® Abhayaahudi.‚ÄĚ 
